Thank you @dunejewelry for my beautiful “Touch the World” bracelets✨ I’m so honored to support a variety of notable causes that help make the world a better place. 

I chose the black semi-colon bracelet in support of mental health awareness since my mom is a clinical psychologist and is always working to help people improve their mental health. It’s handcrafted with sand from Rehoboth Beach, Delaware, to represent the University of Delaware, where she was 1st introduced to the topic of psychology.

I chose the Maroon Staff of Hermes Bracelet in support of humanitarian medical care, with beach sand from Antigua. My aunt is a physician and she honeymooned in Antigua, so this bracelet reminds me of her and her passion to help humankind. 

Dune Jewelry is a woman-owned small business and each experiential design is handcrafted with your choice of beach sand, earth, shells, etc. Use my code “TTW10” for 10% off! 🌊

#DuneJewelry #ExperientialJewelry #WearYourTravels #BostonBusiness #HandcraftedJewelry #JewelryForACause
